1.0.0.name: wordpress/seomoz-widgets
1.0.0.description:
Provides dashboard elements and themes widgets to display SEO related info, like inbound links, retrieved using the SEOmoz Linkscape API. You must have a free SEOmoz.org account and API credentials.

The SEOmoz Inbound Links dashboard widget is similar to the default dashboard widget that queries Google Blog Search, but is more accurate and complete, as it pulls link information from across the entire web, not just from Google Blog Search.
